name: Home (kind of)
narrative: I lived in Shaker until I was 13, when my family moved south to Atlanta. These days my connections to the Cleveland area are few, but I remain an Indians, Browns, and Cavs fan.

name: The University of Kentucky
narrative: UK's New Maps Plus program offers its courses online, so I actually earned this certificate from my couch in Brooklyn. But Lexington is a great town!
